title: Episode #32: Faith, Forgiveness, and the Mind with Dr. David Levy
description: In this episode I interview Dr. David Levy, one of the top neurosurgeons in the U.S, on his journey to find faith and forgiveness. Dr. David will be a guest speaker at my 2018 Conference: https://drleafconference.com
